data.title: Airports Participating in LAANC
data.meta_description: LAANC is available at 541 LAANC Enabled Facilities and 732 airports. The list below shows all airports currently offering the LAANC capability. If you wish to fly in controlled airspace near airports where LAANC is not available, you can use the manual process to apply for an authorization. The list below shows all airports currently covered by the LAANC capability.
data.text:
LAANC is available at 541 LAANC Enabled Facilities and 732 airports. The list below shows all airports currently offering the LAANC capability. If you wish to fly in controlled airspace near airports where LAANC is not available, you can use the manual process to apply for an authorization.

The list below shows all airports currently covered by the LAANC capability.
